OL,3,CEx-councillor jailed for 20 weeks for
OL,4,Cstalking Dame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FAn ex-councillor has been jailed for
OL,7,F20 weeks for stalking former
OL,8,FPortsmouth North MP Dame Penny
OL,9,FMordaunt.
OL,11,FEdward Brandt, 61, was found guilty by
OL,12,Fa jury in November, following a trial
OL,13,Fat Southampton Crown Court, which
OL,14,Fheard that the former Conservative
OL,15,FParty leadership candidate feared
OL,16,F"sexual violence" and believed the 61-
OL,17,Fyear-old was a "real threat".
OL,19,FBrandt was acquitted of a more serious
OL,20,Fcharge of stalking involving serious
OL,21,Falarm or distress.
