OL,3,CEx-councillor jailed for 20 weeks for
OL,4,Cstalking Dame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FSentencing Brandt, Judge William
OL,7,FMousley KC told him: "I am satisfied
OL,8,Fthat there is a real risk of you
OL,9,Freoffending or causing harm to other
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"Also, having regard to the nature of
OL,13,Fthese offences, the appropriate
OL,14,Fpunishment must be by way of immediate
OL,15,Fimprisonment.
OL,17,F"I do not sentence you on the basis of
OL,18,FPenny Mordaunt's person impact
OL,19,Fstatements but it's very clear that
OL,20,Fyour behaviour had a very significant
OL,21,Fand enduring impact on her."
