OL,7,Fdue to the stress, every time I step
OL,8,Fout of the building I am looking over
OL,9,Fmy shoulder and checking to see if he
OL,10,Fis there.
OL,12,F"I am living in a constant fear of a
OL,13,Fconfrontation."
OL,15,FDame Penny, who hit the headlines for
OL,16,Fcarrying ceremonial swords at the
OL,17,FKing's coronation, continued: "It's
OL,18,Fhugely impacted all aspects of my
OL,19,Flife, both my professional life and
OL,20,Fpersonal life, and I cannot stress
